Display clear.
self setContents: 'TOP SELF'.
Transcript show: self contents.
Transcript cr.
self = Workspace ifTrue: [ Transcript show: 'SELFWORK' ] ifFalse: [ Transcript show: 'BADSELF' ].
Transcript cr.
(thisContext receiver = Workspace) ifTrue: [ Transcript show: 'CTXWORK' ] ifFalse: [ Transcript show: 'BADCTX' ].
Transcript cr.
